Enumeration Attribute : 
Name : PxeBootPriority
ReadOnly : False
Display Name : Enable PXE Boot Priority
Help String : When enabled, if a new PXE boot option is detected, it will be added to the top of the Boot Sequence.
When forced, any PXE boot option will be on the top of the Boot Sequence; and any external PXE boot option(s) have the higher boot priority than any internal PXE boot option(s). OS installation will not change the PXE boot option priority.

